</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-74_ pf-text-1"><strong>Quality assurance</strong> - Implementing robust quality assurance processes to maintain high standards of care.<br></li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-76_ pf-text-1"><strong>Record-keeping</strong> - Keeping accurate and detailed records of all veterinary treatments and procedures.
